    <node id="Server Architecture">
      <data key="d0">Server Architecture</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Server Architecture refers to the structural design and organization of server hardware and software systems, serving as both a foundational engineering discipline and a primary analytical taxonomy in computing infrastructure. It encompasses the integration, interconnection, and configuration of core components, including processors, memory subsystems with emphasis on scalable design and hierarchy, storage, I/O interfaces, and high-speed interconnect technologies such as PCIe and HSIO. Modern Server Architecture increasingly incorporates advanced features like hardware-enforced quarantine mechanisms enabled by eSFI and PCIe-MI, reflecting a strategic evolution toward security, reliability, adaptability, and workload-specific optimization—particularly for AI and machine learning applications. This includes tight coupling with AI-optimized hardware organization for large language model inference, utilizing low-latency communication and CXL-enabled memory fabrics.

Beyond its technical definition, Server Architecture functions as a technical domain, design methodology, and classification framework within research documentation. It is consistently identified as a topic tag, technical domain tag, and category tag associated with report documents, indicating the technical focus area, content category, and relevance to server infrastructure. It is the primary subject matter and core topic for reports such as the Mt. Diablo Server Scope report, where it is categorized under the core research library. In Chinese-language technical report libraries, it is explicitly tagged as“研报库/核心】服务器架构”and“【核心】服务器架构”. The domain informs critical decisions in component selection and modular system design, guided by industry initiatives like the Open Compute Project's Component Management Sub-project (OCP CMS). Across all contexts, Server Architecture is affirmed as the unifying conceptual and practical foundation for research, development, and deployment of next-generation server systems.&lt;SEP&gt;The thematic category or tag assigned to the document.&lt;SEP&gt;A core topic tag associated with the document.&lt;SEP&gt;A tag category associated with the report.&lt;SEP&gt;A core topic category associated with the report, indicated by tags in the document metadata.&lt;SEP&gt;Classification category for the report within the library.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3993cd0b737e3130edf76f25d51050ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7cb819bd8f7ecd3c6e4efa0548627c2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-147c4db7a4ce5872858a38c1ac58af56&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c984e299ac9432c7e312cc7b398b600&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3556e182081aed4b9613c75949ed570&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba1d69c721849ac582b1a53a58646ef1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-805ed11febeca1bfd1bdea057549e4ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e24b7488a587cd1f8bf6573d12f1c75a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46bc26dff317560becba9a0a6fa7a441&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d542a9101cecae9b9250937b2605dee2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f1a30530b2b434213d044c2a8466044&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10dc48654563b9bb58e4fbbbb7645eb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e88d373c00da121b8868d08bdceb9cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-207b0823e90b60e301db1f919be31b9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef5a1dc3d7c28f0190c5185e1c92732b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b48c48f2f7c3877c03d05218cfb8c20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ae046aa80e7382953f272a3870f099b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4173aa4ed70cd6d625ee79aebe2a677&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7dd14306d9061dddba8b150d9c7d98b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-97525ceaf715f1ad94448c8abc5642db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0559e293569f15eabf0cd28fac35d14f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef9903a22739411840df5a1652b687d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c461db61ef0a922e7d7292d8516c1147&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03978f9015d72cc2c030ac8e6447fed7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-538e9be43efc9f4740b1699a18d33882&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0849f10e95d7677ebed5f2a29c650a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e43b9c7c8f30976446ff07cfb8acd723&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63f83f5a5cef6dac282d861fd6da9e77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-900ad8221a96dafc212eef7868a063e8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7480ef95765b1d3cb3e7cc5a73e67e91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f023cd84d3e2ed9cf707d62efd5ddbb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54b80862fb010b672af4957bef254768&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b71eacebd07cf22c28bd1377859a2954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55f9a5f9dbd8556e5eeb84b9bb117c15&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fde36569763e8e63f5879815d072c123&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bf489aadb0f21630c59b8361f23e8f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41e5bcd0e2dad86fc34ddddd1afe3ac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa73bfb5833304f96f036b9a9653ece2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1d28fc57f74bd152b123d626835823bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1d26679a5c7d4be95dc3163cdd74635d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-846347bde485d