    <node id="File Path">
      <data key="d0">File Path</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">File Path refers to a set of Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) strings using the “file://” scheme that denote the local filesystem locations of technical PDF documents stored on a macOS system. All identified file paths share the common base directory `/Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/`, indicating a curated personal library focused on advanced server architecture—particularly AI infrastructure, memory systems, high-density computing, and related hardware acceleration technologies. The collection includes reports with titles such as “Efficient AI Serving at Scale – Processing Near Memory Acceleration for LLMs and Vector Search”, “Towards Memory Efficient RAG Pipelines with CXL Technology”, “Memory Technology Optimized for At-Scale AI Systems”, “Rack Architecture for Next Generation AI Server”, “Flash Memory Chiplet Implementation and Applications”, “Super Fluid Technology Application in High Density Server Product”, “Short-reach Optical Interface Scale Connectivity for Optimized Data-movement Through Memory for AI-ML Applications”, and “Community Panel – Enabling Immersion by Design – Aligning Server and Cooling Communities”. Specific examples include `file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/93%20-%20Use%20Cases%20for%20CXL%20RAS%20Firmware-First%20Error%20Handling_v2.pdf`, `file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/75%20-%20Architecting%20the%20AI%20Fabric-Scalable%20Networking%20for%20Next-Generation%20AI%20Servers-Racks-and%20Clusters_v2_v2.pdf`, `file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/7137%20-%20Server%20Scale-Up%20Interconnect%20Technologies%20-%20UALink%20SuperNode%20and%20CXL%20Memory%20Pool_v2.pdf`, `file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/[2025]_20250807%20DRAM%20304%201%20An.pdf`, `file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/[2025]_20250806%20CXLT%20203%201%20Kim%20Updated%20copy.pdf`, `file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/[2025]_20250807%20CXLT%20302%201%20Pan%20copy.pdf`, and `file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/Mt.%20Diablo%20Server%20Scope.pdf`. These paths employ percent-encoding for spaces and special characters (e.g., `%20`), and many filenames contain version indicators such as `_v2`, `_v2_v2`, or `_v2_v2_v2`, reflecting iterative revisions. Collectively, the File Path set represents a domain-specific, locally maintained repository of technical resources addressing hardware-software co-design challenges in large-scale AI systems—including CXL-based memory pooling, UALink interconnects, optical I/O, DRAM and flash chiplet integration, thermal management (e.g., “Super Fluid Technology”), rack-level architecture, and firmware-first reliability mechanisms.&lt;SEP&gt;The file path "file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/Interconnects%20and%20Connectivity%20for%20At%20scale%20AI%20Shaping%20the%20Future%20of%20Interconnects%20and%20Memory%20Fabric%20for%20Open%20AI%20Systems.pdf" specifies the local storage location of the report.&lt;SEP&gt;The file path "file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/DC%20Memory%20Fabric%20management%20An%20In%20Depth%20Review%20of%20the%20K8s%20OCP%20Reference%20Implementation.pdf" specifies the local storage location of the report.&lt;SEP&gt;The file path "file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/[2026]_02%2002%20谈谈大模型架构的演进之路,%20The%20Art%20of%20memory..md" specifies the local storage location of the report.&lt;SEP&gt;The file path “file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/Lifecycle%20System%20Monitoring%20with%20Arm’s%20System%20Monitoring%20Control%20Framework%20SMCF%20and%20proteanTecs.pdf” is a digital artifact specifying the local location of the report.&lt;SEP&gt;The file path "file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/Memory%20technology%20optimized%20for%20at%20scale%20AI%20systems%20Bandwidth%20Capacity%20and%20Connectivity.pdf" specifies the local storage location of the report.</data>
