    <node id="CXL Technology">
      <data key="d0">CXL Technology</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">CXL (Compute Express Link) is a high-speed interconnect technology designed to enable memory pooling and sharing across CPUs, GPUs, and accelerators, supporting memory-efficient AI workloads.&lt;SEP&gt;CXL Technology is a high-speed interconnect standard designed to enable memory pooling, sharing, and coherent communication between CPUs, accelerators, and memory devices.</data>
