    <node id="Local Document Link">
      <data key="d0">Local Document Link</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Local Document Link refers to a file system hyperlink that uses the file:// URI scheme to reference PDF documents stored on a local machine. These links are typically embedded in digital interfaces with descriptive anchor text such as “点击打开本地文档” (“Click to open local document”) and are intended for direct access to locally saved files rather than remote web resources. The links point to specific, absolute file paths on the user’s filesystem—most commonly on Liufang’s machine—and include percent-encoded characters to handle spaces, special symbols, and non-ASCII Unicode (e.g., Chinese characters in directory names like “【核心】服务器架构”). Two distinct PDF documents are explicitly identified via their full file URIs: one titled “7026 - Emerging Software Patterns for Programming New Memory Devices and Interfaces_v2_v2.pdf” and another titled “Super Fluid Technology Application in High Density Server Product.pdf”, both residing under the /Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【核心】服务器架构/ directory. While the exact filename and path vary across instances, all Local Document Links share core technical characteristics: they are local, file-based, URI-formatted references to PDFs, and they assume the target file exists at the specified location on the author’s or user’s local storage. The link’s functionality depends on client-side support for the file:// protocol and appropriate file system permissions.&lt;SEP&gt;The local document link is a file path pointing to the PDF document on the user's system: file:///Users/liufang/Documents/Library/【重复归档】/[2015]_End%20To%20End%20Memory%20Networks.pdf.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-93d5d66acecc3b09726280461a1741c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e24b7488a587cd1f8bf6573d12f1c75a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61f77d89f092ff5cd7c6ea81d31cfeb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c8929bd6af5efae83044622ffa3faac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ae046aa80e7382953f272a3870f099b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71812bc0fbded857fe0a4b82f5223b84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-11fbfb718c91a1cacf50d05e7bcc41bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-266b57d952795e78de135dd7ea0d1822&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41e5bcd0e2dad86fc34ddddd1afe3ac0</data>
